{"tid":694637,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[重建啦，GDP又升] 紅雨KO高鐵西九站 漏水如瀑布 工程員：10號波點算？","createTime":"2018-06-08T13:31:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-08T17:51:16.000Z","uid":51271,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"8a1288e8af377d216593dd7fdfd47651848bdfc0","tid":694637,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T13:31:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180608/58295360\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180608%2F58295360&d=MWM9e7Lkmcv0%2FiCloJa%2BCHadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=4003c7e8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180608%2F58295360&h=c18a96e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180608/58295360</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180608/large/1528464267_b05c.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180608%2Flarge%2F1528464267_b05c.jpg&d=MWM9e7Lkmcv0%2FiCloJa%2BCHadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=8b38cfcd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180608/large/1528464267_b05c.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n 港鐵工程醜聞不絕。繼沙中線紅磡站月台駁位爆出造假風波，耗資超過800億的高鐵香港段工程亦安全成疑。高鐵西九龍站在今早暴雨期間多處漏水，要用沙包及膠布圍封。有工程人員透露，站內有四層出現漏水，「好似瀑布咁漏」，斥工程已淪「千億豆腐渣」工程，「3號風球就咁，8號、10號（風球）點算？」<br />\n<br />\n天文台今早一度發出3號強風信號及黃雨、紅雨警告信號，至下午才陸續取消。不過，高鐵西九龍站疑「受不住」風吹雨打，多處出現漏水。有港鐵工程人員向《蘋果》透露，西九龍站地下車站大廳、B1售票大堂、B2及B3層，至少共6、7處地方漏水，「今朝係好似瀑布咁漏，滴雨水落嚟」，情況持續超過1小時。該名工程人員估計，疑因玻璃天幕未有接駁好，令雨水滲漏至天花，再流到地面。<br />\n<br />\n該工程人員續稱，事發後有保安在漏水位置把守，禁止其他人拍照及使用電話，「可能係上次（沙中線紅磡站月台）剪短螺絲頭之後，驚人影相俾傳媒知」。而地盤工人及職員等未有因漏水一事需要停工。他批評，高鐵香港段造價近千億，卻出現如此嚴重的「甩漏」是不能接受，斥已淪為「千億豆腐渣」工程，「（漏水情況）太誇張，3號風球已經咁，8號、10號（風球）點算？」<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》正向港鐵查詢，正等候回覆。據該名工程人員提供的照片，指在今早暴雨信號期間所拍，其中B1層近的士站地上有大片水漬，由沙包及鐵馬圍封，中間放有水桶及大型垃圾桶，未知是否用作「裝水」；B3層鄰近關口前的入閘機則由大片膠布遮蓋，並以膠帶圍封；地下車站大廳的漏水位置亦放有多個沙包及膠布等。"},{"pid":"2a10a2b6f38f6e3f3f72d1481f2701cb60237a9f","tid":694637,"uid":51271,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T13:31:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180608/large/1528464267_b05c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180608%2Flarge%2F1528464267_b05c.jpg&h=3212a2eb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2a4e398ef6a8c7bfa3ad167520ba7fb162ec952e","tid":694637,"uid":35667,"like":61,"dislike":3,"score":58,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T13:32:59.000Z","msg":"漏水咁小事 快d通車啦<br />\n我地班老友記要搭呀"},{"pid":"d194225285fb6e66eed747ffd900b2ce6178033a","tid":694637,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T13:33:01.000Z","msg":"有排爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cdbc301069126fadaeba80a75fb0ceec2d0480d","tid":694637,"uid":151933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T13:39:19.000Z","msg":"幾時又有水舞間睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebd068df8ea332423f82a486303c96d45a877ed9","tid":694637,"uid":13115,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T13:40:35.000Z","msg":"千億工程用黎懲罰港豚<br />\n一流"},{"pid":"fabbdb1eb7e0491b84b23d870806167c7c0ebc16","tid":694637,"uid":66527,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T13:40:47.000Z","msg":"好想快d打風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe28cc2224a3c0538bc77a46682933da40b90d17","tid":694637,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T13:44:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"656381b3900a1b600012d1b208f81956b2d0e695","tid":694637,"uid":9694,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyT